        {
            "id": 6432429,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Atlassian Corporation - Class A(TEAM-US)大漲5.04%，報71.03美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Atlassian Corporation - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TEAM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TEAM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TEAM-US</a>)截至台北時間25日02:10股價上漲3.41美元，報71.03美元，漲幅5.04%，成交量2,984,985（股），盤中最高價71.03美元、最低價68.32美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.25%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.72%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.56%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+4.4%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Atlassian Corporation - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TEAM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TEAM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TEAM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.62%</li> <li>近 1 月：-9.13%</li> <li>近 3 月：-48.68%</li> <li>近 6 月：-59.02%</li> <li>今年以來：-58.3%</li></ul></section></main>",
